@startuml activity_manage_system
title Activity Diagram - ManageSystem

start
:System Administrator logs in and opens Admin Panel;
:Select administrative category;
if (Category?) then (Users & Roles)
  :Manage user accounts & roles (RBAC);
elseif (Master Data) then (Shared Lists)
  :Manage shared catalogs (merchandise, units);
elseif (Operation Logs) then (View Logs)
  :Query cross-department operations;
else (Backup & Restore)
  :Trigger backup or restore process;
endif
:Submit request;
if (Data is valid & Authorized?) then (yes)
  :System executes operation and persists changes;
  :Log administrative action;
  :Show success confirmation;
  stop
else (no)
  :Display Validation/Authorization Error;
  stop
endif
@enduml
